data.description: Take a look at this charming home 2 Bed. 1.75 Bath with concrete around the home. Updated flooring, Kitchen, Bathrooms, and exterior paint. By the side of the house there is a storage room. The home comes with a smart alarm system as well.  Don't miss out on this lovely home.
